negeri.\",\"juz_id\":24,\"surah_id\":40,\"transliteration\":\"mâ yujâdilu fî âyâtillâhi illalladzîna kafarû fa lâ yaghrurka taqallubuhum fil-bilâd\",\"translation_en\":\"No one disputes concerning the signs of Allāh except those who disbelieve, so be not deceived by their [uninhibited] movement throughout the land.\",\"translation_de\":\"Über Allahs Zeichen streiten nur diejenigen, die ungläubig sind. Lasse dich durch ihren Wechsel in den Landstrichen nicht täuschen.\",\"translation_tr\":\"İnkâr edenler müstesna, hiç kimse Allah’ın âyetleri hakkında tartışmaz. Onların şehirlerde (rahatlıkla) gezip dolaşması seni aldatmasın.\",\"translation_fr\":\"Il n’est que les mécréants qui disputent au sujet des Signes d’Allah. Que leurs multiples activités dans le pays ne te leurrent point.\",\"tajweed\":[{\"class\":\"madd-jaiz\",\"start\":16,\"end\":20},{\"class\":\"madd-arid-lissukun\",\"start\":105,\"end\":106}]},\"surah\":\"$20\",\"index\":3}],[\"$\",\"$L1f\",\"4\",{\"verse\":{\"id\":4138,\"number\":5,\"text\":\"كَذَّبَتْ قَبْلَهُمْ قَوْمُ نُوحٍ وَّالْاَحْزَابُ مِنْۢ بَعْدِهِمْۖ وَهَمَّتْ كُلُّ اُمَّةٍ ۢ بِرَسُوْلِهِمْ لِيَأْخُذُوْهُ وَجَادَلُوْا بِالْبَاطِلِ لِيُدْحِضُوا بِهِ الْحَقَّ فَاَخَذْتُهُمْۗ فَكَيْفَ كَانَ عِقَابِ\",\"translation_id\":\"Sebelum mereka, kaum Nuh dan golongan-golongan yang bersekutu setelah mereka mendustakan (rasul). Setiap umat telah merencanakan (tipu daya) terhadap rasul mereka untuk membunuhnya. Mereka membantah dengan (alasan) yang batil untuk melenyapkan kebenaran. Maka, Aku menyiksa mereka. Bagaimanakah (pedihnya) azab-Ku?\",\"juz_id\":24,\"surah_id\":40,\"transliteration\":\"kadzdzabat qablahum qaumu nûḫiw wal-aḫzâbu mim ba‘dihim wa hammat kullu ummatim birasûlihim liya'khudzûhu wa jâdalû bil-bâthili liyud-ḫidlû bihil-ḫaqqa fa akhadztuhum, fa kaifa kâna ‘iqâb\",\"translation_en\":\"The people of Noah denied before them and the [disbelieving] factions after them, and every nation intended [a plot] for their messenger to seize him, and they disputed by [using] falsehood to [attempt to] invalidate thereby the truth. So I seized them, and how [terrible] was My penalty.\",\"translation_de\":\"(Schon) vor ihnen haben das Volk Nuhs und nach diesen die Gruppierungen (ihre Gesandten) der Lüge bezichtigt. Jede Gemeinschaft hatte vor, (gegen) ihren Gesandten (vorzugehen, um ihn) zu ergreifen. Und sie stritten mit dem Falschen, um damit die Wahrheit zu widerlegen. Da ergriff Ich sie. Wie war da Meine Bestrafung!\",\"translation_tr\":\"Onlardan önce Nuh kavmi ve bunlardan sonraki topluluklar da (peygamberlerini) engellemeye, her ümmet kendi peygamberini yakalamaya azmetmişti. Bâtılı hakkın yerine koymak için mücadele etmişlerdi. Bunun üzerine ben onları kıskıvrak yakaladım. İşte, cezalandırmamın nasıl olduğunu gör!\",\"translation_fr\":\"Avant eux, le peuple de Noé avait crié au mensonge, imité ensuite par les coalisés. Chaque communauté a comploté pour se saisir de son Messager. En disputant, tous mobilisaient de faux arguments pour réfuter la vérité. J’ai alors sévi contre eux, et comme fut (terrible) Mon châtiment !\",\"tajweed\":[{\"class\":\"qalqalah\",\"start\":12,\"end\":13},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":31,\"end\":36},{\"class\":\"iqlab\",\"start\":52,\"end\":54},{\"class\":\"iqlab\",\"start\":55,\"end\":57},{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":72,\"end\":74},{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":86,\"end\":88},{\"class\":\"iqlab\",\"start\":89,\"end\":91},{\"class\":\"iqlab\",\"start\":92,\"end\":94},{\"class\":\"qalqalah\",\"start\":153,\"end\":154},{\"class\":\"madd-arid-lissukun\",\"start\":211,\"end\":212}]},\"surah\":\"$20\",\"index\":4}],[\"$\",\"$L1f\",\"5\",{\"verse\":{\"id\":4139,\"number\":6,\"text\":\"وَكَذٰلِكَ حَقَّتْ كَلِمَتُ رَبِّكَ عَلَى الَّذِيْنَ كَفَرُوْٓا اَنَّهُمْ اَصْحٰبُ النَّارِۘ\",\"translation_id\":\"Demikianlah (sebagaimana berlaku kepada umat terdahulu), ketetapan Tuhanmu itu berlaku pula bagi orang-orang yang kufur bahwa mereka adalah para penghuni neraka.\",\"juz_id\":24,\