ang, puis vous fait sortir enfants pour que vous atteigniez ensuite la maturité et la vieillesse. Il en est parmi vous qui décèdent avant cela mais vous (tous) parviendrez jusqu’à un terme (déjà) nommé. Peut-être y méditerez-vous.\",\"tajweed\":[{\"class\":\"idgham-mimi\",\"start\":22,\"end\":27},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":28,\"end\":33},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":36,\"end\":41},{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":41,\"end\":43},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":47,\"end\":52},{\"class\":\"qalqalah\",\"start\":53,\"end\":54},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":57,\"end\":62},{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":62,\"end\":64},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":77,\"end\":82},{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":82,\"end\":84},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":103,\"end\":105},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":106,\"end\":108},{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":109,\"end\":111},{\"class\":\"qalqalah\",\"start\":117,\"end\":118},{\"class\":\"madd-jaiz\",\"start\":123,\"end\":126},{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":142,\"end\":144},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":166,\"end\":168},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":170,\"end\":172},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":175,\"end\":179},{\"class\":\"idgham-mimi\",\"start\":179,\"end\":184},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":185,\"end\":190},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":202,\"end\":207},{\"class\":\"qalqalah\",\"start\":207,\"end\":208},{\"class\":\"qalqalah\",\"start\":218,\"end\":219},{\"class\":\"madd-jaiz\",\"start\":224,\"end\":227},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":233,\"end\":235},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":236,\"end\":238},{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":242,\"end\":244},{\"class\":\"idgham-bighunnah\",\"start\":246,\"end\":248},{\"class\":\"madd-arid-lissukun\",\"start\":270,\"end\":272}]},\"surah\":\"$20\",\"index\":66}],[\"$\",\"$L1f\",\"67\",{\"verse\":{\"id\":4201,\"number\":68,\"text\":\"هُوَ الَّذِيْ يُحْيٖ وَيُمِيْتُۚ فَاِذَا قَضٰىٓ اَمْرًا فَاِنَّمَا يَقُوْلُ لَهٗ كُنْ فَيَكُو